{"name":"Incendiary Spelldust","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>You complete the material component of a multi- component spell but haven’t completed the spell yet.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You quickly add a dash of charged alchemical powder set to react with the spell’s material components. At the end of your turn, the space where you cast this spell erupts in flames. These flames deal fire damage equal to the spell’s level to any creature who ends their turn in the space, with a basic Reflex save against your Crafting DC. The flames die after 1 minute.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"incendiary-spelldust","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":4},"traits":{"value":["manipulate"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"skill","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"free"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Alchemical Crafting"},{"value":"ability to cast a spell"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.6","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685648397531,"modifiedTime":1685727698511,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"16MoyJbtRfAPg3Kc"}
{"name":"Seeking Spelldust","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>You complete the material component of a multi- component spell but haven’t completed the spell yet.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>With a quick flourish, you sprinkle the remains of your spell’s material components on the ground around you.</p>\n<p>Attempt a secret Thievery check. Your GM compares the results against the Stealth DC of the nearest creature who is hidden to you. If no creatures in this encounter are hidden to you, use a standard DC for your level.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The spelldust falls into a revelatory symbol. You learn whether there is a hidden creature, and the direction to them. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus on your attempts to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.BlAOM2X92SI6HMtJ]{Seek} them.</p>\n<p><strong>Success </strong>As critical success, but no circumstance bonus.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure </strong>The spelldust dismisses and you learn nothing.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> Your spelldust fails you. You learn false information determined by your GM.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"seeking-spelldust","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":4},"traits":{"value":["detection","divination","manipulate","secret"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"skill","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"free"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"expert in Thievery"},{"value":"ability to cast a spell"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.6","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685648397531,"modifiedTime":1685727693460,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"UI5gcJFCozKohz67"}
{"name":"“Last Chance”","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>You complete one component of a multi- component spell that targets a single creature but haven’t completed the spell yet, or you succeeded at @UUID[Item.1sZLSnOWXfbJfaeZ]{Test Spell}.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You give your target a chance to surrender. Attempt an Intimidation check against the target’s Will DC. If you critically succeeded at @UUID[Item.1sZLSnOWXfbJfaeZ]{Test Spell}, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to this check.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target releases any weapons they’re holding and can’t take hostile actions for 1 minute. You can choose to not finish casting the spell or choose a different target for the spell. Continuing to cast the spell against the target negates the effects of this free action and grants your target a +4 circumstance bonus to their defense against the spell.</p>\n<p><strong>Success </strong>As critical success, but they can’t take hostile actions for 1 round.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"last-chance","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":4},"traits":{"value":["linguistic"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"skill","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"free"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"expert in Intimidation"},{"value":"ability to cast a spell"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.6","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685648397531,"modifiedTime":1685727704694,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"cIeYPdPvoyfJzrwl"}
{"name":"Diplomatic Runes","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>You complete the somatic component of a multi- component spell but haven’t completed the spell yet.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You have learned to augment your spell runes with bright, visual messages without disrupting the flow of your spellcasting. Choose a language you know and a creature who can see you. Attempt to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.OX4fy22hQgUHDr0q]{Make an Impression} on the creature. If the creature doesn’t know the language you chose, you automatically fail.</p>\n<p>If the creature does know the language, after resolving your check to Make an Impression, they become immune to your @UUID[Item.EUrnVDDFK0pvqqQp]{Diplomatic Runes} for 1 day. If you succeed or critically succeed, you can choose to not complete the spell or to select a different target. Continuing to cast the spell against the same target negates the effects of this free action and grants your target a +4 circumstance bonus to their defense against the spell.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"diplomatic-runes","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":4},"traits":{"value":["linguistic","manipulate","visual"],"rarity":"common"},"category":"skill","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"free"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"expert in Diplomacy"},{"value":"ability to cast a spell"},{"value":"two languages besides Common"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.6","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685648397531,"modifiedTime":1685727709898,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"eWCKscKn0ctvCjP2"}
{"name":"Test Spell","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>You complete one component of a multi- component spell that targets a single creature but haven’t completed the spell yet.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You send out your mind along magical threads to test the target’s weaknesses. Attempt a spell attack roll. If the spell you’re casting targets a DC, use the same DC for this roll. If the spell would require the target to make a save, use their relevant save DC. This attack roll doesn’t increase your multiple attack penalty, and your multiple attack penalty doesn’t apply.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> You learn the value of the DC.</p>\n<p><strong>Success </strong>You learn that you succeeded.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure </strong>You learn that you failed. You can choose to not finish casting the spell or choose a different target for the spell.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"test-spell","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":4},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"category":"skill","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"expert in a skill you can Recall Knowledge with"},{"value":"ability to cast a spell"}]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.6","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685648397531,"modifiedTime":1685727657463,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"weRSAa1mnrCTG4DU"}
